      "text": [
        " اَلرِّضَا عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"اَلْمُتْعَةُ لاَ تَحِلُّ إِلاَّ لِمَنْ عَرَفَهَا وَ هِيَ حَرَامٌ عَلَى مَنْ جَهِلَهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4584 - Imam Ali ibn Musa Ar-Ridha (as) said:\n\"Temporary marriage (Mutah) is not lawful except for one who understands it, and it is forbidden for one who is ignorant of it.\""
        ]
      }
